WEBVTT

00:00:00.294 --> 00:00:06.987
her Avrom Sherman, mit ayer erloybenish geyen mir vayter mit undzer intervyu, mit kasete numer tsvey.

00:00:07.904 --> 00:00:13.124
ir hot oyfgehert bay dertseyln di frierdike kasete vegn der,

00:00:12.579 --> 00:00:14.973
vegn dos lebn in Apt, in OPATOW.

00:00:13.124 --> 00:00:15.003
dos lebn in Apt.

00:00:15.194 --> 00:00:18.682
zayt azoy gut un dertseylt zhe vayter vos hot pasirt.

00:00:20.830 --> 00:00:25.468
ikh vil yetst prubirn tsu dertseyln vi azoy es, vos hot pasirt

00:00:25.468 --> 00:00:27.085
in nayntsn nayn un draysik.

00:00:27.580 --> 00:00:29.667
ikh bin shoyn geven a yingl

00:00:30.044 --> 00:00:32.755
fun, ikh veys, zibetsn yor, mistam.

00:00:36.322 --> 00:00:38.020
in a, a fraytik,

00:00:38.465 --> 00:00:39.725
ho'mir gehert,

00:00:40.220 --> 00:00:43.015
hobn mir gezen in droysn oyf di,

00:00:43.291 --> 00:00:48.027
se iz gevezn an ⟨runde⟩ fun beton vos me hot oyfgehongen di MODAOT,

00:00:48.202 --> 00:00:49.850
az se hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome.

00:00:49.940 --> 00:00:51.287
frier hot men shoyn gefilt

00:00:51.287 --> 00:00:54.457
az se geyt oysbrekhn a milkhome, vayl me hot gehert di,

00:00:54.530 --> 00:00:57.697
di ale geshreyen fun fun dem Hitler,

00:00:58.175 --> 00:01:00.028
un me hot gehert di

00:01:00.028 --> 00:01:04.194
di, me hot, di mobilizatsye, me hot mobilizirt mentshn a sakh.

00:01:04.554 --> 00:01:06.370
un me hot gevust az,

00:01:06.629 --> 00:01:11.230
me hot alts nisht gegloybt az mamesh mamesh oysbrekhn a milkhome? se iz, se iz epes...

00:01:11.962 --> 00:01:13.705
ober leyder iz, se iz

00:01:13.705 --> 00:01:15.010
fraytik in der fri,

00:01:15.084 --> 00:01:19.229
erklert, Daytshland hot erklert krig Poyln.

00:01:21.648 --> 00:01:23.077
vos hot pasirt?

00:01:24.314 --> 00:01:25.810
bald shabes

00:01:27.082 --> 00:01:28.207
hobn mir gehert

00:01:28.465 --> 00:01:30.046
eroplanen flien,

00:01:30.625 --> 00:01:32.662
undz zenen ale arop in di kelers.

00:01:33.646 --> 00:01:36.712
me hot zikh opge- tsugegreyt esn un me iz gelign in di kelers untn.

00:01:36.970 --> 00:01:41.167
ober yedn mol hot men gehert a, a bombe, an a ⟨eksplozye⟩.

00:01:41.544 --> 00:01:45.234
zenen aropgelofn bombes in a, vos hobn gehat UNK tsu bombardirn,

00:01:45.830 --> 00:01:47.866
zey hobn gemakht mamesh griber!

00:01:48.057 --> 00:01:50.060
zenen geharget gevorn derbay mentshn,

00:01:51.483 --> 00:01:56.894
di eyntsike feler vi azoy zey hobn ge- se iz geharget gevorn, veys ikh nisht tsi se iz azoy vikhtik, ober dos iz dos, se iz gesheen do.

00:01:57.490 --> 00:02:02.244
se iz zey hobn, zey hobn aropgevorfn bombes in azelkhene pletser, tsum bayshpil lebn der mikve.

00:02:02.502 --> 00:02:03.982
lebn di yidishe mikve,

00:02:04.055 --> 00:02:05.956
lebn di, lebn a shule,

00:02:06.670 --> 00:02:09.213
in mitn a gas, in mitn a...

00:02:09.421 --> 00:02:11.643
zenen gefaln a sakh bombes in Apt.

00:02:11.851 --> 00:02:13.702
mir zenen gelegn in di kelers.

00:02:14.247 --> 00:02:16.134
azoy zenen mir geze-,

00:02:16.134 --> 00:02:18.089
se hot gedoyert dakht zikh mir

00:02:19.023 --> 00:02:20.472
fir oder finef tog,

00:02:20.472 --> 00:02:22.021
vos me hot moyre gehat aroystsugeyn.

00:02:22.803 --> 00:02:24.873
me hot afile nisht gevust vos in droysn pasirt.

00:02:25.165 --> 00:02:26.847
mir hobn zikh gehat tsugegreyt esn,

00:02:27.933 --> 00:02:29.193
un

00:02:30.447 --> 00:02:32.585
ikh denk az se iz gevezn donershtik,

00:02:32.709 --> 00:02:34.537
dem zibetn tog fun der milkhome,

00:02:34.582 --> 00:02:36.601
ober dem zibetn,

00:02:36.742 --> 00:02:39.369
yo, dem zibetn september, se iz gevezn,

00:02:39.594 --> 00:02:41.309
zenen ongekumen daytshn.

00:02:44.859 --> 00:02:50.540
zenen ongekumen daytshn un zey hobn bald, azoy vi zey zenen arayngekumen in shtetl hobn zey bald farbrent dem gantsn mark.

00:02:51.170 --> 00:02:53.054
untergetsundn di gantse reye,

00:02:53.499 --> 00:02:56.362
eyn helft di mar- di mark. vos heyst bay di mark?

00:02:56.485 --> 00:02:59.349
yede shtetl in in Poyln hot zikh gehart a mark.

00:02:59.793 --> 00:03:03.764
vu eyn mol in der vokh zenen tsuzamengekumen di ale poyerim di derfer

00:03:03.764 --> 00:03:05.165
un me hot dort gemakht a yerid.

00:03:05.193 --> 00:03:08.008
me hot oyfgetoysht skhoyres, me hot farkoyft, me hot gekoyft,

00:03:08.008 --> 00:03:10.250
poyerim hobn zikh ⟨opgegreyt⟩ far a gantse vokh,

00:03:10.357 --> 00:03:14.317
zey hobn gebrengt zeyer produktn. dos iz geven der yerid, mitvokh.

00:03:14.575 --> 00:03:18.265
un dos iz geven a ma- der mark. se iz geven zeyer a groyse plats.

00:03:20.532 --> 00:03:23.463
un dos, eyn helft fun dem, hobn zey bald farbrent.

00:03:24.515 --> 00:03:26.824
vo- far vos hobn dos getun,

00:03:26.844 --> 00:03:31.074
farshtanen mistam ontsuvarfn a moyre az me zol nisht prubirn epes tsu makhn.

00:03:32.176 --> 00:03:36.035
un me hot ongehoybn aroystsukrikhn fun di, fun di kelers.

00:03:37.745 --> 00:03:41.705
un di daytshn zenen arayngekumen un me hot ge⟨UNK⟩ di gantse shtot fil mit daytshn.

00:03:42.774 --> 00:03:49.158
un zey hobn gezogt az yeder eyner zol zikh ongeyn mit, zey hobn aroysgeshtelt farshidene MODAOT,

00:03:49.203 --> 00:03:52.876
az yeder eyner zol zikh opgeyn normal mit zeyer lebn, mit zayn lebn.

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:56.996
un azoy hot zikh dos shtetl ongehoybn langzam, lang tsurik tsu normalizirn.

00:03:57.033 --> 00:04:00.717
mentshn hobn gearbet, poyerim zenen ts- arayngekumen in shtot arayn,

00:04:00.717 --> 00:04:01.567
se iz gevezn

00:04:01.690 --> 00:04:03.254
mer veynik normal.

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:09.245
in nayntsn fertsik hot men ongehoybn filn a bisl shoyn

00:04:09.723 --> 00:04:10.949
nisht azoy fray.

00:04:11.090 --> 00:04:12.226
koydem kol

00:04:12.226 --> 00:04:13.677
hot men gekhapt tsu der arbet,

00:04:13.677 --> 00:04:15.103
nisht aroys in droysn,

00:04:15.103 --> 00:04:17.682
nor mamesh in di shtot okopes tsu makhn,

00:04:18.481 --> 00:04:21.161
tsu reynikn di gasn, tsu hakn shteyner,

00:04:21.161 --> 00:04:23.127
tsu reynikn stam, stam

00:04:23.127 --> 00:04:25.310
mentshn, me hot gekhapt mentshn tsu der arbet.

00:04:25.771 --> 00:04:27.909
far nakht hot men zey tsurik aheymgelozt.

00:04:30.007 --> 00:04:33.022
un ende fe- nayntsn, ende nayntsn fertsik

00:04:33.820 --> 00:04:38.135
iz gevezn a farordenung az yeder yid muz ontun a pask- a,

00:04:38.326 --> 00:04:39.232
a band,

00:04:39.845 --> 00:04:41.797
mit a mogn-doved, oyf der hant.

00:04:43.085 --> 00:04:46.775
dos iz gevezn di ershte gezeyre mamesh vos me hot derkent dem yidn.

00:04:48.772 --> 00:04:51.635
ober mir zenen ongeganen mit undzer arbet.

00:04:52.602 --> 00:04:54.000
farkert di sh-

00:04:54.000 --> 00:05:00.210
Apt iz gevezn a shtot fun mamesh, keyn industrye iz kimat in Apt nisht, bloyz eyn fabrik

00:05:00.210 --> 00:05:01.417
iz gevezn in Apt,

00:05:01.417 --> 00:05:03.886
vos hot, vos hot produtsirt zeyf un likht.

00:05:04.060 --> 00:05:06.049
se iz geven der hoypt industrye in Apt.

00:05:06.049 --> 00:05:07.194
mer iz nisht gevezn.

00:05:07.452 --> 00:05:09.455
di fabrik hot gehert tsu a yidn?

00:05:09.190 --> 00:05:09.877
yo.

00:05:10.287 --> 00:05:11.244
Mandelbaum.

00:05:11.570 --> 00:05:15.192
dos iz der eyntsiker raykher yid in Apt, vos me hot gezogt, me hot gedenkt oyf im,

00:05:16.143 --> 00:05:18.191
un dortn hobn gearbet

00:05:18.191 --> 00:05:22.803
ikh veys, polyakn un yidn, mistam efsher a hundert oder hundert fuftsik mentshn,

00:05:22.859 --> 00:05:24.001
hobn dortn gearbet.

00:05:27.348 --> 00:05:31.527
un me hot, ober der hoypt iz gevezn bay undz in shtot, bershtn.

00:05:33.541 --> 00:05:39.577
se iz gevezn, oyb ikh gedenk, iz gevezn di tsveyte shtot in a- in Poyln vos hot zikh farnumen mit bershtn.

00:05:39.768 --> 00:05:41.737
eyn shtot iz gevezn Mezritsh,

00:05:42.350 --> 00:05:43.638
un di tsveyte shtot iz

00:05:43.638 --> 00:05:44.960
gevezn OPATOW.

00:05:45.050 --> 00:05:47.924
kimat yede tsveyte drite

00:05:47.952 --> 00:05:50.157
balebos hot zikh gehat zayn varshtatl,

00:05:50.332 --> 00:05:54.556
un gearbet barshtn. di barshtn zenen gegan oyf, koydem kol zenen zey gegan oyf gants Poyln,

00:05:54.584 --> 00:05:55.929
un oykhet oyf oysland.

00:05:56.120 --> 00:05:59.096
zenen gemakht gevorn farshidene, farshidene sortn barshtn.

00:05:59.096 --> 00:06:03.387
fun a kleyn bershtele tsu putsn di sh- biz groyse bershtl ts- far di ferd.

00:06:04.034 --> 00:06:09.412
yedn fals iz, a sakh zenen gevezn, eyner mit a klener fabrikl, eyner mit a gresere fabrikl,

00:06:09.620 --> 00:06:11.363
eyner hot gehat a bisl mer mentshn,

00:06:11.363 --> 00:06:13.884
mayn zeyde hot oykh gehat a fabrikl fun barshtn.

00:06:13.974 --> 00:06:17.228
mayne tsvey feters, di mame's tsvey brider, hobn gearbet,

00:06:17.228 --> 00:06:19.329
un me hot gehaltn etlekhene meydlekh

00:06:19.329 --> 00:06:22.608
vos hobn arayngetsoygn do di hor in di, in di lekhlekh fun di barshtn.

00:06:24.453 --> 00:06:26.416
un azoy hot men gearbet, nor

00:06:26.416 --> 00:06:28.632
di daytshn hobn ongehoybn tsu bashteln

00:06:29.937 --> 00:06:33.259
ah barshtn, bay di barshtn-makher, azoy ze'mir gevezn farnumen.

00:06:33.259 --> 00:06:36.305
un bay di shusters hobn zey bashtelt shtivl, shikh,

00:06:36.316 --> 00:06:39.697
shnayders zenen geven farnumen mit, zey hobn bashtelt bay shnayders

00:06:39.708 --> 00:06:41.272
farshidene

00:06:41.885 --> 00:06:43.432
ikh veys, mundirn.

00:06:43.741 --> 00:06:49.389
shtetl iz geven farnumen mer veynikstns, azoy az me hot koym koym getsoygn dos bisl khayune.

00:06:50.592 --> 00:06:55.627
dos iz gevezn nayntsn fertsik. in nayntsn eyn un fertsik iz shoyn gevezn, iz shoyn gevorn a bisl erger.

00:06:55.672 --> 00:06:58.653
koydem kol hot men, hot zikh yeder eyner gemuzt opshern di bord.

00:06:59.317 --> 00:07:03.361
a farordenung az ver se vet, me vet trefn a yid in droysn mit a bord, vet men im shisn.

00:07:04.615 --> 00:07:06.908
se iz shoyn gevezn faln fun etlekhe geshosene,

00:07:06.908 --> 00:07:08.525
nisht azoy fil, ober

00:07:09.003 --> 00:07:13.936
er aleyn ⟨iz⟩ aroysgegangen fun di shtot, me UNK me hot nisht getort geyn, yedn fals zenen gevezn geshosene,

00:07:13.936 --> 00:07:16.051
di urzakhn veyst keyner nisht mistam.

00:07:18.335 --> 00:07:22.177
ikh hob aykh gevolt nor fregn a frage, far dem vi mir geyen foroys,

00:07:22.604 --> 00:07:30.361
bald vi di daytshn zenen arayngegangen, oder far arayngang fun di daytshn, iz geven faln vi yidishe khevre, yidishe bokhurim hobn antlofn?

00:07:31.143 --> 00:07:33.688
dos iz gevezn, dos iz gevezn, yo.

00:07:33.688 --> 00:07:35.322
zet oys, gut ir hot mikh dermant.

00:07:35.902 --> 00:07:38.140
yidishe bokhurim zenen antlofn nokh Rusland.

00:07:38.399 --> 00:07:40.531
me hot ongehoybn tsu loyfn mamesh nokh Rusland.

00:07:40.531 --> 00:07:43.231
vayl me hot gedenkt az dortn iz es ganeydn

00:07:43.231 --> 00:07:45.054
un a sakh zenen geven komunistn,

00:07:45.099 --> 00:07:48.839
zey hobn zikh nakher leyder ibertsaygt az se iz nisht gevezn di rikhtike plats,

00:07:49.014 --> 00:07:51.404
ober a sakh dafke hobn zikh geratevet.

00:07:51.579 --> 00:07:53.564
ober a sakh zenen ober tsurikgekumen.

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:57.794
zey hobn gezen az se iz dortn, az me ha- bahandlt zey nisht dortn als komunistn,

00:07:57.794 --> 00:07:59.082
nor als farreter,

00:07:59.814 --> 00:08:03.200
hobn zey oysgedreyt dem ⟨dishl⟩ un zenen gekumen aheym tsurik.

00:08:04.235 --> 00:08:10.659
un a sakh zenen geganen mit, a sakh zenen geganen in di lagern, a sakh zenen geganen mit di, in di oyvns arayn.

00:08:10.850 --> 00:08:14.034
zenen take gevezn a sakh vos z-, gut vos ir hot mikh dermant, zenen antlofn.

00:08:15.642 --> 00:08:20.800
ober nokh a zakh hob ikh fargesn tsu zogn az in nayntsn, ende nayntsn fertsik,

00:08:21.717 --> 00:08:23.551
zenen gekumen zeyer a sakh

00:08:24.097 --> 00:08:28.659
mentshn fun di groyse shtet, in di kleyne shtetlekh, me hot gemeynt az in di kleyne shtetlekh

00:08:28.659 --> 00:08:29.964
vet men zikh kenen rateven.

00:08:30.459 --> 00:08:34.739
se zenen ongekumen azoy fil mentshn az me hot kimat tsu yedn eynem arayngegebn a familye.

00:08:35.757 --> 00:08:40.983
mir hobn gekrign a familye mit tsvey kinder, a froy mit a froy mit tsvey, a froy mit a man mit tsvey kinder,

00:08:41.427 --> 00:08:45.027
un me hot mit- me hot gemuzt opgebn eyn tsimer, un mir hobn gehat

00:08:45.055 --> 00:08:47.986
di tsveyte tsimer. me hot gemakht a ventl far g- far,

00:08:48.430 --> 00:08:50.281
az me iz opgesheydt,

00:08:50.911 --> 00:08:54.939
un di gantse varshtat mitn shlof-tsimer mit di kokh ho'mir gehat in eyn tsimer.

00:08:55.366 --> 00:08:57.217
un zey hobn oykh gevoynt in eyn tsimer.

00:08:57.729 --> 00:09:00.046
zenen geven oyf Lodzhe, zey zenen dafke gevezn Lo-

00:09:00.046 --> 00:09:02.499
zenen leyder geganen mit ale tsuzamen.

00:09:02.892 --> 00:09:05.435
dos iz gevezn in Apt, se iz gevorn shreklekh eng.

00:09:05.896 --> 00:09:09.991
se iz vayle, me hot gemuzt araynnemen, yeder eyner hot gemuzt araynnemen a familye.

00:09:09.963 --> 00:09:17.112
az ir zogt, "me hot gemuzt araynnemen," heyst dos se iz geven epes a yidishe makht vos hot gefirt mit dem? vos kent ir mir dertseyln vegn dem?

00:09:14.519 --> 00:09:15.352
yo.

00:09:15.352 --> 00:09:15.965
yo.

00:09:16.308 --> 00:09:19.424
yo, se iz gevezn, koydem kol hot men geshafn a yidishn komitet,

00:09:19.734 --> 00:09:21.444
un me hot

00:09:21.489 --> 00:09:26.444
der firer funem m- komitet iz gevezn a gevise Mordkhe Vaysblum.

00:09:26.838 --> 00:09:30.140
gevezn a mer inteligenter mentsh, er iz shoyn gevezn far di krig

00:09:30.280 --> 00:09:32.384
fun dem onfirer fun dem komitet.

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:34.831
un er hot

00:09:35.140 --> 00:09:41.328
un er hot dos farteylt di mentshn, veyst az yeder eyner hot, me hot prubirt nisht arayntsunemen, yo arayntsunemen.

00:09:41.418 --> 00:09:44.157
ober se hot leyder nisht geholfn, me hot gemuzt araynnemen,

00:09:44.157 --> 00:09:44.841
me hot.

00:09:44.841 --> 00:09:47.369
se iz geven a komitet vos hot zikh farnumen mit dem.

00:09:47.847 --> 00:09:51.920
se iz dokh, se hot zikh oykh geshafn a kokh vos me hot geholfn yidishe kinder,

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:54.288
a bisl shpeter tsu, ven se iz shoyn gevezn,

00:09:54.395 --> 00:09:55.554
ven di,

00:09:56.133 --> 00:09:58.206
me hot shoyn tsugebrengt a bisl mer...

00:09:58.206 --> 00:10:01.409
zey zenen gegangen sistematish. zey hobn nisht gemakht mit eyn mol,

00:10:02.157 --> 00:10:03.252
azoy az me,

00:10:03.252 --> 00:10:06.725
me hot nisht gegloybt, zey zenen gegangen mit aza sistem az der,

00:10:06.832 --> 00:10:11.045
az der, dem yid hot nisht gegloybt az me darf, az me ⟨hoft⟩ shteln a vidershtand.

00:10:11.371 --> 00:10:12.699
se vet ibergeyn!

00:10:12.839 --> 00:10:16.023
se vet zikh endikn mit di milkhome vet vider vern ales normal.

00:10:16.180 --> 00:10:19.398
ay se zenen gefaln mentshn do dortn? dos iz dokh a milkhome.

00:10:19.994 --> 00:10:21.325
ober ales,

00:10:21.361 --> 00:10:24.328
shpeter ales, in nayntsn,

00:10:24.348 --> 00:10:28.696
ende nayntsn eyn un fertsik, umg- onheyb tsvey un fertsik, ho'mir shoyn gefilt

00:10:28.955 --> 00:10:31.998
vos zey geyen tun, ober se hot shoyn, me hot shoyn leyder gornisht gekent tun.

00:10:31.998 --> 00:10:34.602
me hot shoyn undz arayngenumen in tsvey dray gasn,

00:10:35.587 --> 00:10:39.142
un me hot undz arumgeringlt mit, mit a tsoym,

00:10:39.232 --> 00:10:44.373
un ver se iz aroys fun di, fun dem shtetl, fun di, fun dem geto, hot dos geheysn,

00:10:44.598 --> 00:10:46.502
iz me, iz dershosn gevorn.

00:10:46.370 --> 00:10:48.226
ven hot dos pasirt?

00:10:48.496 --> 00:10:51.809
genoy, genoy dem tog g- vey- gedenkt keyner nisht.

00:10:51.809 --> 00:10:53.654
ober se hot pasirt

00:10:53.997 --> 00:10:57.704
ende eyn un fertsik, anfang tsvey un fertsik, umgefer azoy.

00:10:58.452 --> 00:11:01.352
vayl ikh denk, ikh veys fun onfang tsvey un fertsik

00:11:01.352 --> 00:11:03.492
iz shoyn di lage geven zeyer zeyer shlekht.

00:11:03.785 --> 00:11:06.952
mentshn zenen mamesh oysgegangen far hunger, vayle me hot nisht gehat,

00:11:07.801 --> 00:11:11.305
tsu undz, ikh veys nisht vi, ikh ken zikh nisht dermanen vi azoy andere,

00:11:11.480 --> 00:11:13.974
bay undz, undz undz hobn gehat a polyak eynem,

00:11:13.974 --> 00:11:16.286
Kalita hot er geheysn, ikh ken zikh dermanen dem nomen,

00:11:16.323 --> 00:11:17.872
er hot arayngeganvet,

00:11:17.875 --> 00:11:21.937
vayl azoy vi er iz gevezn undzer, undzer's a arayngeyer un er hot gevoynt in a dorf,

00:11:22.111 --> 00:11:24.890
flegt er, flegt er araynbrengen a bisl kartofl,

00:11:25.570 --> 00:11:26.476
geheym,

00:11:26.853 --> 00:11:28.724
araynkumen in

00:11:28.724 --> 00:11:30.762
geto ze- hobn polyakn gemegt,

00:11:31.510 --> 00:11:35.153
ober zey aleyn hobn oykh moyre gehat arayntsugeyn, shoyn, se iz shoyn gevorn azoy shlekht

00:11:35.189 --> 00:11:36.925
az zey hobn moyre gehat az me vet zey nisht kenen aroy-

00:11:36.925 --> 00:11:39.557
ober er iz arayngekumen, er hot gebrengt tsu undz a bisl esn, a bisl,

00:11:39.557 --> 00:11:41.157
azoy hot men nokh getsoygn,

00:11:41.247 --> 00:11:43.379
ober se iz gevezn zeyer, mamesh,

00:11:43.379 --> 00:11:44.769
oysgeganen far hunger.

00:11:45.787 --> 00:11:47.199
se iz gevezn zeyer shlekht.

00:11:47.930 --> 00:11:49.193
un

00:11:49.193 --> 00:11:52.599
mentshn zenen, koydem kol hot me, hot men shoyn ongehoybn mer tsu shisn,

00:11:52.739 --> 00:11:54.944
ayedn kleynikeyt mamesh hot men geshosn.

00:11:56.401 --> 00:11:58.201
se iz se iz se hot se,

00:11:58.274 --> 00:11:59.939
di lage iz gevezn zeyer shlekht.

00:12:00.974 --> 00:12:03.973
ver hot gevakht oyf dem fun droysn?

00:12:03.649 --> 00:12:06.099
d- maystn hobn gevakht ukrainer.

00:12:07.927 --> 00:12:10.284
in ayer gegnt hobn gelebt ukrainer?

00:12:08.939 --> 00:12:09.645
oykhet,

00:12:09.665 --> 00:12:12.005
neyn, me hot zey gebrengt fun Ukraine.

00:12:12.078 --> 00:12:15.582
vi azoy hobn undz gebrakht, hobn gehitn, in Daytshland ukrainer?

00:12:16.330 --> 00:12:18.822
ikh, hob ikh aykh, ikh hob aykh gezogt az dos shpeter,

00:12:18.895 --> 00:12:22.113
az d- mir hobn gelitn am maystn fun ukrainer, yedn fals ikh.

00:12:24.954 --> 00:12:29.574
ober es zenen gevezn dortn in di shtot, zenen arumgeganen daytshn mamesh, daytshn.

00:12:29.577 --> 00:12:34.010
se dermant in bukh di nemen velkhe zey hobn, zenen geven spetsyele sadistn.

00:12:34.437 --> 00:12:38.063
ikh gedenk nisht keyn nemen, ober se iz do mentshn vos zey gedenken nemen, zey hobn oyfgegebn,

00:12:38.099 --> 00:12:42.256
azoy vi mir tsuzamengeshtelt dos bukh, hot yeder eyner geshribn vos er hot gedenkt,

00:12:42.284 --> 00:12:46.599
vayl dos iz nokh gevezn mit etlekhe draysik yor tsurik, der zikorn iz nokh gevezn a bisl mer

00:12:47.515 --> 00:12:49.518
klor, vi azoy er iz yetst,

00:12:49.709 --> 00:12:54.564
iz vos eyner vos hobn gedenkt, un se iz do mentshn vos hobn gedenkt mer eyntslheytn, eltere fun mir,

00:12:54.924 --> 00:13:00.065
hobn gedenkt az, mentshn, di nemen fun di sadistn, nemen fun di daytshn.

00:13:00.864 --> 00:13:03.198
ikh hob keyn nemen nisht gedenkt, iber hoypt nisht.

00:13:03.209 --> 00:13:04.908
ikh, biz yetst.

00:13:05.437 --> 00:13:09.734
zayendik in geto, fun ende ts- eyn un fertsik, azoy vi ir hot gezogt,

00:13:11.714 --> 00:13:16.315
gevakht hobn di geto, loyt dem vos ir zogt, ukrainer mit di daytshn,

00:13:15.595 --> 00:13:17.007
ukrainer un oykhet polyakn.

00:13:16.945 --> 00:13:18.813
polyakn, ukrainer un daytshn.

00:13:17.131 --> 00:13:17.795
polya-

00:13:17.806 --> 00:13:22.520
polyake- polya- di poylishe politsey hot oykh geholfn bavakhn.

00:13:22.548 --> 00:13:24.112
hobn oykh getun a mitsve,

00:13:24.303 --> 00:13:27.068
zikh mishtadl tsu zayn

00:13:27.068 --> 00:13:27.959
in dem fal.

00:13:28.066 --> 00:13:31.371
in geto vos ho- vi hot, vi hot zikh gefirt der ordenung in geto,

00:13:31.371 --> 00:13:32.313
gedenkt ir?

00:13:32.707 --> 00:13:36.332
der ordenung in geto vos, koydem kol me hot geshafn

00:13:36.332 --> 00:13:37.294
a kokh

00:13:37.314 --> 00:13:39.704
far kinder vos zenen nebekh oysgegangen far hunger.

00:13:40.503 --> 00:13:44.142
un vifl me hot gekent hot men tsuzamgenu- koydem kol hot men,

00:13:45.211 --> 00:13:47.680
hot men tsuzamen, se iz gevezn farshidene faln

00:13:47.725 --> 00:13:51.348
vos di daytshn hobn farlangt benzin. fun vanen hot men gekent hobn benzin?

00:13:53.615 --> 00:13:56.174
tomer nisht hobn zey aroysgenumen azoy fil un azoy fil, geshosn.

00:13:56.669 --> 00:13:58.908
zey hobn farlangt farshidene fleyshn, zog-

00:13:59.302 --> 00:14:03.616
zogt er, vi ken men hobn fleysh? fun vanen UNK nemen fleysh, undz ze'mir ayngeshpart.

00:14:03.706 --> 00:14:06.097
yedn fals, hobn mir prubirt tsu shafn gelter,

00:14:06.693 --> 00:14:13.285
un se zenen gevezn azelkhene vos hobn gehat a kontakt fu- mitn droysn, mit oyser un me hot gemuzt shafn, me hot geshafn.

00:14:13.105 --> 00:14:15.682
ver hot UNK, ver hot dos organizirt?

00:14:14.590 --> 00:14:19.479
se iz gevezn eyner, se se iz geven eyner, a Henekh Langer hot er geheysn, er iz gevezn zeyer

00:14:19.602 --> 00:14:21.267
a ongezeener yid.

00:14:21.594 --> 00:14:24.662
koydem kol hot er gearbet mit di, mit di IRIYA,

00:14:24.662 --> 00:14:26.873
mit di poylishe IRIYA far di milkhome.

00:14:26.909 --> 00:14:28.113
er iz gevezn, un er hot

00:14:28.113 --> 00:14:30.144
gehat a tsutrit tsu di daytshn.

00:14:30.369 --> 00:14:32.911
un az zey hobn epes badorfn zenen zey gekumen tsun im.

00:14:33.693 --> 00:14:35.780
un mir zenen gekumen tsun im veynen.

00:14:36.207 --> 00:14:40.086
ober vos er hot gekent hot er getun, vos er hot gekent helfn, vos er hot gekent

00:14:40.086 --> 00:14:41.754
opshrayen a gezeyre

00:14:42.265 --> 00:14:46.462
hot er, hot er geholfn. vos er hot nisht gekent leyder hot er nisht gekent, er iz,

00:14:46.872 --> 00:14:49.679
zenen geven feler, tsum bayshpil, ikh hob fargesn tsu dermanen,

00:14:49.724 --> 00:14:52.452
az az azoy vi zenen arayngekumen di daytshn,

00:14:52.525 --> 00:14:54.325
hobn zey bald genumen a

00:14:54.702 --> 00:14:56.893
akhtsik oder nayntsik, me- mener

00:14:56.913 --> 00:14:59.202
un farshpart in dem kino zal.

00:15:00.052 --> 00:15:03.455
farshpart, mamesh zey gehaltn dortn UNK dort tsu zayn, etlekhe teg.

00:15:03.629 --> 00:15:07.353
un me hot farlang fun di shtot epes azoy fil un azoy fil gelt, oder vos.

00:15:07.595 --> 00:15:09.631
me hot tsuzamengenumen un me hot zey aroysgelozt.

00:15:10.649 --> 00:15:11.589
dos iz eyn fal.

00:15:11.695 --> 00:15:13.681
yetst, redndik vegn geto,

00:15:13.484 --> 00:15:14.103
yo

00:15:15.391 --> 00:15:26.054
hot ir shoyn gezogt az se iz geven eyner vos iz geven der rosh kehile, der yudnra- der hoypt oyf dem yudnrat, un akhuts dem hot ir dermant dem yidn vos flegt zayn der farbinderung mit di daytshn, den.

00:15:25.199 --> 00:15:30.132
yo, ober er iz oykh gevezn in yudnrat. se iz gevezn etlekhene mentshn.

00:15:29.166 --> 00:15:33.116
akhuts do vos ir dermant, se iz geven oykh yidishe politsey ⟨in ⟩?

00:15:32.367 --> 00:15:33.155
yo.

00:15:33.116 --> 00:15:34.842
vos gedenkt ir? vos

00:15:33.481 --> 00:15:38.184
zenen gevezn yidishe politsey vos hobn zikh zeyer zeyer nisht azoy sheyn oyfgefirt.

00:15:38.274 --> 00:15:40.625
vayl yeder eyner hot ge- hot dokh gedor-,

00:15:40.625 --> 00:15:42.166
se hot zikh im gedokhtn az me vet,

00:15:42.391 --> 00:15:46.098
me vet zayn a bayshtayerung vet er blaybn lebn. ober leyder se iz,

00:15:47.015 --> 00:15:51.363
yeder eyner hot zikh gevolt rateven oyf oyf oyf dem oyfn vi er hot, vi er hot gedenkt er ken zikh rateven.

00:15:51.672 --> 00:15:54.597
iz eyner gevorn a, di zelbe zakh mit kapos in di lagern.

00:15:54.597 --> 00:15:56.577
zey hobn gedenkt az zey veln iberlebn.

00:15:56.127 --> 00:15:59.986
ir gedenk epes faln vegn vi hobn zikh oyfgefirt di yidishe politsey?

00:15:59.334 --> 00:16:03.803
faln, spetsyele spetsifishe faln gedenk ikh nisht, ober me hot geredt, me hot gevust.

00:16:03.803 --> 00:16:05.774
se iz do a v- eyner afile lebt nokh

00:16:06.050 --> 00:16:07.276
in Kanade.

00:16:07.653 --> 00:16:09.818
vos me hot geke- me hot im gornisht getun, ober,

00:16:09.818 --> 00:16:13.503
er hot nisht geharget keyn mentshn kholile, ober er hot zikh nisht oyfgefirt azoy vi

00:16:14.605 --> 00:16:16.051
azoy vi

00:16:16.293 --> 00:16:20.585
azoy vi darf zikh oy- zenen gevezn etlekhe mosrim oykhet vos zey hobn tsugetrogn,

00:16:20.585 --> 00:16:22.396
vos hobn gedenkt az zey ⟨hobn⟩,

00:16:22.773 --> 00:16:25.552
vos eyn moser iz gevezn dafke a lodzher,

00:16:26.182 --> 00:16:31.458
vos zey hobn im geshosn nakher. er hot ge- tsugetrogn zakhn vu mentshn hobn bahaltn

00:16:32.071 --> 00:16:34.313
vu mentshn hobn bahaltn skhoyres.

00:16:34.313 --> 00:16:36.683
yo, se iz nokh gevezn a fal vos me hot ongehoybn,

00:16:36.683 --> 00:16:38.579
vos iz gevezn nokh nayntsn fertsik,

00:16:39.091 --> 00:16:43.270
az yeder eyner hot gemuzt tsushteln in di shul arayn a futer vos er hot gehat.

00:16:45.132 --> 00:16:47.709
dos lebn iz nokh gevezn azoy,

00:16:48.153 --> 00:16:49.601
me hot zikh nokh gevitslt,

00:16:49.601 --> 00:16:51.204
mit dos. ikh gedenk a fal

00:16:51.939 --> 00:16:56.568
se iz bay undz geven a yid, dafke a groyser oreman, a balegole, ober a groyser

00:16:56.759 --> 00:17:00.635
kh- khush aro- khush-humor, hot er gehat.

00:17:01.957 --> 00:17:03.220
aza kluger yid gevezn.

00:17:03.220 --> 00:17:05.799
brengt er dos peltsl, tsu yedn fals iz a,

00:17:06.648 --> 00:17:09.984
veyst dokh, keyn keyn tsu reyne peltslekh iz im UNK nisht gevezn.

00:17:10.344 --> 00:17:12.616
geven krikhndik a sakh dort in di peltslekh.

00:17:13.600 --> 00:17:17.982
brengt er dos in shul arayn, UNK er flegt forn oyf yeridim mitn vogn,

00:17:18.376 --> 00:17:20.716
un nemt dos peltsl un git dos aleyn avek.

00:17:20.890 --> 00:17:22.437
zogn dortn di shomrim,

00:17:22.865 --> 00:17:24.187
far vos leygstu nisht di,

00:17:24.187 --> 00:17:26.355
oyf di kupe leyg, azoy vi yeder eyner. zogt er,

00:17:26.392 --> 00:17:28.107
se vet shoyn, zogt er, aleyn tsugeyn.

00:17:29.868 --> 00:17:33.288
dos iz nor, dos hobn mir zikh nokh gevitslt, dos iz nokh geven nayntsn fertsik.

00:17:33.429 --> 00:17:34.523
ikh vil aykh der-

00:17:34.523 --> 00:17:38.654
dertseyln az der, dos lebn iz nokh geven mer veynikstn a bisl normal,

00:17:38.710 --> 00:17:39.644
az me hot nokh gehat,

00:17:39.644 --> 00:17:42.066
me hot nokh organizirt farshidene

00:17:42.066 --> 00:17:45.050
anshtaltn, teater, gezangen,

00:17:44.600 --> 00:17:45.708
in in geto?

00:17:45.545 --> 00:17:46.467
nisht in geto.

00:17:46.439 --> 00:17:47.429
farn geto.

00:17:47.064 --> 00:17:50.230
farn geto. se iz geven nayntsn fertsik. in geto hot men shoyn gornisht gekent tun.

00:17:50.540 --> 00:17:51.474
geto iz ge-

00:17:51.474 --> 00:17:54.460
geto hot yeder eyner gekemft far a tog teglekhn ekzistents.

00:17:54.505 --> 00:17:55.920
keyner hot shoyn nisht gehat,

00:17:55.940 --> 00:17:59.684
me hot shoyn nisht ge- koydem kol, mentshn hobn shoyn nisht gehat dem mut, mentshn zenen gevezn,

00:17:59.684 --> 00:18:01.615
hobn gekemft farn,

00:18:01.615 --> 00:18:03.022
oyf ibertsulebn.

00:18:03.804 --> 00:18:06.363
fun tsayt tsu tsayt hot men gekhapt grupes,

00:18:06.639 --> 00:18:09.007
grupn yid- a yunger khevre,

00:18:09.018 --> 00:18:10.565
tsu der arbet aroys,

00:18:10.992 --> 00:18:13.824
a grupe hot men gekhapt nokh Maydanek, nokh Belzhets,

00:18:13.827 --> 00:18:15.664
me hot zey nakher tsurik aheymgeshikt.

00:18:15.700 --> 00:18:16.921
ober nakher

00:18:16.949 --> 00:18:18.361
hobn zey nokh a mol genumen,

00:18:18.485 --> 00:18:20.049
hobn shoyn mit mir tsuzamen.

00:18:20.881 --> 00:18:26.579
az ir hot dermant Maydanek, Belzhets, ir hot zhe yene tsaytn nokh nisht gevust vos es meynt,

00:18:26.399 --> 00:18:29.578
me hot UNK me hot zey gekhapt oyf arbet, me me hot gezogt oyb me,

00:18:29.589 --> 00:18:35.590
az geyn forn avek oyf arbet un me vet zey tsurikbrengen. me darft hobn arbeter tsu k- makhn okopes, o-

00:18:35.782 --> 00:18:39.961
ober leyder zey hobn zey geboyt, Maydanek hobn zey geboyt krematoryes.

00:18:39.882 --> 00:18:41.952
ober ober demolts hot ir nisht gevust vegn

00:18:41.502 --> 00:18:43.285
ver hot gevust? keyner hot nisht gevust.

00:18:43.595 --> 00:18:45.378
me hot nor gevust demolt,

00:18:46.210 --> 00:18:52.111
ven zenen antlofn etlekhe fun di, dos iz shpeter, zenen antlofn fun di dos.

00:18:52.420 --> 00:18:53.911
ober keyner hot gornisht gevust.

00:18:53.911 --> 00:18:57.168
se hot zikh keyner nisht gekent forshteln az me vet nemen mentshn,

00:18:57.168 --> 00:18:59.739
lebedike mentshn, vos yeder eyner iz a velt far zikh,

00:18:59.879 --> 00:19:03.620
yeder eyner hot a familye, mentshn, me zol umbrengen, mamesh umbrengen mentshn!

00:19:04.385 --> 00:19:05.729
⟨vemets hot es⟩?

00:19:06.106 --> 00:19:09.012
di kinder in geto hobn zikh nokh gekent lernen?

00:19:10.308 --> 00:19:16.445
in geto i- k- se iz gevezn, me hot ayngefirt farshidene private, ke- keyn shuln iz nisht gevezn keyn.

00:19:18.037 --> 00:19:19.803
koydem kol in di geto,

00:19:19.944 --> 00:19:23.161
a shule, keyn private, yidishe shule iz dokh nisht gevezn.

00:19:23.842 --> 00:19:28.109
me hot ayngefirt grupn vos me hot gelernt kinder, vayl me hot dokh alts gedenkt se vet ibergeyn.

00:19:28.109 --> 00:19:29.877
un se iz geven a shod di tsayt

00:19:29.984 --> 00:19:31.990
me zol farlirn bay yunge kinder.

00:19:31.990 --> 00:19:33.522
ober shuln,

00:19:34.051 --> 00:19:35.736
di, fun der regirung

00:19:35.739 --> 00:19:36.942
zenen nisht gevezn

00:19:36.942 --> 00:19:37.775
in der milkhome.

00:19:38.050 --> 00:19:39.108
nisht in geto.

00:19:39.434 --> 00:19:42.503
se ken zayn, dos gedenk ikh nisht, ken zayn iz oyser der geto iz nokh,

00:19:42.503 --> 00:19:45.132
hot nokh ekzistirt a shule. dos gedenk ikh nisht.

00:19:44.800 --> 00:19:46.543
ober nisht far keyn yidishe kinder.

00:19:45.965 --> 00:19:49.395
yidishe, yidishe nisht. me hot dokh nisht gekent aroysgeyn.

00:19:50.150 --> 00:19:53.317
yetst, ir hot dermant etlekhe mol vegn

00:19:53.390 --> 00:19:55.510
shvern hunger in geto,

00:19:55.668 --> 00:20:02.514
vi BKHOL ZOT, hobn zikh a eytse gege- se iz geven epes a kikh, me hot epes tsugeholfn, me hot geteylt epes, portsyes?

00:20:01.333 --> 00:20:03.090
bloyz far kinder hot men geteylt.

00:20:03.090 --> 00:20:05.045
vi me hot genumen di esns,

00:20:05.304 --> 00:20:08.921
ikh veys bay undz vi azoy se iz gevezn. undz hot geholfn a po- a polyak,

00:20:08.949 --> 00:20:10.777
er hot arayngebrengt a bisl esn,

00:20:10.777 --> 00:20:13.719
zenen, flegn nokh araynkumen polyakn afile in geto,

00:20:13.842 --> 00:20:16.835
a sakh vos hobn gemuzt arayngekumen, vayl zey hobn badorfn a,

00:20:16.880 --> 00:20:18.460
a- an antsug tsu der arbet,

00:20:18.871 --> 00:20:24.012
se iz geven a UNK, demolt iz gevezn khaki, hot es geheysn, haynt iz es JEANS.

00:20:24.727 --> 00:20:29.575
vos hobn, dos ho'mir dortn geha- dos iz nokh produktn vos zey hobn nisht gehat in di derfer,

00:20:29.575 --> 00:20:31.015
vos yidn hobn nokh gehat.

00:20:31.325 --> 00:20:34.242
ober di maystn pola- di maystn gesheftn

00:20:34.242 --> 00:20:37.209
hot men arayngeshte- hobn di daytshn arayngeshtelt zeyer mentshn,

00:20:37.450 --> 00:20:39.200
un zey zenen geven di balbatim.

00:20:41.163 --> 00:20:45.697
vi azoy mentshn hobn zikh dernert, mit vos, vi azoy zey hobn arayngekrign in geto,

00:20:46.057 --> 00:20:48.110
ikh ken zikh beshum oyfn nisht dermanen.

00:20:48.639 --> 00:20:52.666
ober se iz, se se iz gevezn dos lebn iz geven zeyer shver.

00:20:52.570 --> 00:20:56.041
me fleg nisht tseteyln keyn portsyes dortn, broyt, oder vos?

00:20:52.925 --> 00:20:53.628
se

00:20:54.376 --> 00:20:58.522
neyn, se iz nisht geven ver zol tseteyln. neyn, dos nisht. yeder eyner hot gekent far zikh.

00:20:59.067 --> 00:21:00.884
keyn organizirte hilf,

00:21:01.413 --> 00:21:06.318
ikh shtel mir nisht for se hot gekent zayn a organizirte hilf, vayl zey hobn aleyn nisht gehat. fun vanen hot me gekent organizirn?

00:21:07.201 --> 00:21:09.676
hilf ken nor zayn az me ken araynbrengen fun droysn.

00:21:10.171 --> 00:21:13.169
mistam iz nokh gevezn mentshn vos hobn bahaltn zakhn,

00:21:13.344 --> 00:21:17.270
tsum bayshpil bay undz hot gevoynt dort in hoyz, hot gevoynt eyner vos hot farkoyft leder.

00:21:17.579 --> 00:21:21.759
flegt er in geheym farkoyfn far a poyer a shti- a shtik leder oyf s- oyf shikh.

00:21:22.574 --> 00:21:24.627
far dem flegt er krign epes a h-

00:21:24.937 --> 00:21:27.007
a halb zak kartofl, oder vi azoy.

00:21:27.164 --> 00:21:30.500
se iz, keyn fleysh iz, gedenk ikh iber hoypt nisht se iz gevezn.

00:21:31.315 --> 00:21:33.723
ir dermant zikh vegn epes

00:21:33.880 --> 00:21:36.001
bazundere aktsyes in geto?

00:21:37.542 --> 00:21:40.861
di aktsyes zenen nor gevezn vos me hot genumen mentshn aroys tsu der arbet.

00:21:41.643 --> 00:21:45.147
keyn andere aktsyes, aktsyes fun farnikhtung zenen geven shpeter, alts tsuzamen.

00:21:45.220 --> 00:21:48.303
biz vi lang zent ir perzenlekh geven in geto?

00:21:48.309 --> 00:21:50.514
ikh bin geven in geto biz

00:21:51.684 --> 00:21:53.889
yuli, nayntsn tsvey un fertsik.

00:21:54.434 --> 00:21:56.892
vos pasirt yuli nayntsn tsvey un fertsik?

00:21:56.274 --> 00:21:56.971
oh.

00:21:56.999 --> 00:21:59.542
yus- in yuli nayntsn tsvey un fertsik

00:21:59.784 --> 00:22:02.579
iz aroysgegangen a ge- bafel az ale

00:22:03.699 --> 00:22:05.431
mener un froyen fun

00:22:05.622 --> 00:22:07.794
fuftsn biz finef un fertsik

00:22:07.884 --> 00:22:11.810
muzn zikh tsushteln oyf a gevisn plats dortn, se iz geven UNK Veg hot es geheysn.

00:22:12.524 --> 00:22:13.700
muz zikh tsushteln.

00:22:14.650 --> 00:22:16.923
zelbst-farshtendlekh az nisht ale hobn zikh tsugeshtelt.

00:22:17.992 --> 00:22:20.905
ikh tsufel- hobn, ikh mit mayn tatn hobn zikh yo tsugeshtelt.

00:22:21.620 --> 00:22:25.816
un se hobn zikh tsugeshtelt demolt, ikh denk aza toyznt tsvey hundert mentshn.

00:22:28.302 --> 00:22:31.253
ikh gedenk nokh mayn mame nokhgelofn, zi hot undz gegebn epes a,

00:22:31.253 --> 00:22:33.311
a in epes in a zekele epes

00:22:33.314 --> 00:22:35.013
⟨bis⟩ zisvarg mit,

00:22:35.457 --> 00:22:38.877
dos ken ikh, dos far- dos letste mol vos ikh hob gezen mayn mame.

00:22:38.934 --> 00:22:41.544
un ikh hob, ikh mitn tatn zenen aroysgeganen,

00:22:42.072 --> 00:22:45.189
me hot zikh tsugeshtelt tsu der grupe, me iz geshtanen dortn UNK,

00:22:46.173 --> 00:22:47.652
ikh denk a gantsn tog.

00:22:49.126 --> 00:22:50.369
un

00:22:52.029 --> 00:22:54.757
nakher hobn zey undz ongelodnt oyf oytos,

00:22:55.876 --> 00:22:57.372
me iz geforn etlekhe sho,

00:22:58.357 --> 00:23:01.068
un zey hobn, me iz ongekumen in a lager,

00:23:01.816 --> 00:23:05.084
vos hot gehe- dos iz gevezn a lager in SKARZYSKO.

00:23:06.625 --> 00:23:09.489
in SKARZYSKO iz geven, zenen geven dray lagers.

00:23:10.557 --> 00:23:12.459
dos iz geven a firme HASAG,

00:23:12.650 --> 00:23:16.441
vos hobn produtsirt amunitsye far di Vermakht, far di daytshn.

00:23:17.425 --> 00:23:23.326
tsi se iz geven privat, tsi tsi mit a regirung, dos veys ikh nisht, ober azoy hot geheysn di lager.

00:23:23.787 --> 00:23:28.405
di lagers zenen gevezn a radyus fun tsen kilometer umgefer, eyner fun tsveytn opgerukt.

00:23:29.744 --> 00:23:36.809
mi- ikh mit mayn tatn zenen ongekumen, azoy ven mir zenen ongekumen in lager, zenen, dos iz geven, se hot geheysn DARKAR, dos iz geven der hoypt lager.

00:23:36.933 --> 00:23:38.824
der hoypt, der hoypt lager.

00:23:38.461 --> 00:23:39.779
vi hot dos geheysn?

00:23:39.520 --> 00:23:43.070
v- zenen geven ayngeteylt VERK A, VERK B, un VERK C.

00:23:43.413 --> 00:23:45.365
A. B. C. di dray lagern.

00:23:48.644 --> 00:23:50.984
un azoy ven mir zenen ongekumen dortn,

00:23:52.340 --> 00:23:56.986
hot men undz bald ge- mikh mitn, mikh hot men genumen tsu makhn epes okopes arum dem lager.

00:23:57.014 --> 00:23:59.135
un andere hobn gearbet bay

00:23:59.259 --> 00:24:02.791
produtsirn bombes, se iz geven opteylungen fun bombes,

00:24:02.791 --> 00:24:06.256
opteylungen fun koyln, makhn koyln, farshidene amunitsye.

00:24:07.207 --> 00:24:08.799
un dos iz

00:24:08.799 --> 00:24:11.398
se iz geven a groyse, a groyse, se iz nisht geven eyn fabrik.

00:24:11.398 --> 00:24:13.414
se iz geven a shetekh fun etlekhene,

00:24:13.417 --> 00:24:15.135
fun a gantse reye fabrikn.

00:24:15.135 --> 00:24:17.765
hales vos me hot oysgearbet farshidene zakhn.

00:24:18.614 --> 00:24:20.431
ikh bin dortn geven fir vokhn.

00:24:21.078 --> 00:24:23.064
un me hot mikh avekgeshikt nokh VERK C.

00:24:24.672 --> 00:24:27.232
VERK C dos iz gevezn mamesh a toytn-lager.

00:24:27.558 --> 00:24:29.324
se iz gevezn oykhet a HASAG,

00:24:30.292 --> 00:24:32.632
me hot dortn, dortn hot men vider produtsirt

00:24:32.958 --> 00:24:35.517
bombes, un mines.

00:24:36.772 --> 00:24:39.331
dos iz a zeyer a interesante kapitl.

00:24:40.923 --> 00:24:43.114
se iz gevezn dortn eyn hale vos,

00:24:43.114 --> 00:24:44.506
a hal- vos heyst a hale?

00:24:44.506 --> 00:24:46.182
a fa- a a hale vos,

00:24:46.340 --> 00:24:49.186
oyf di hales zenen gevezn finef presn,

00:24:49.833 --> 00:24:53.911
un bay di, yede pres hobn gearbet fir mentshn. dos iz zeyer interesant.

00:24:54.929 --> 00:24:56.375
vos hot men dortn gemakht?

00:24:57.562 --> 00:24:58.993
di hale hot geheysn hale,

00:24:58.993 --> 00:25:00.492
di di hale draytsn.

00:25:00.734 --> 00:25:02.638
iz geven zeyer barimt nakher,

00:25:02.641 --> 00:25:06.314
ikh veys nisht in di geshiktn fun ver se hot gegebn eydes,

00:25:06.539 --> 00:25:11.647
iz di hale draytsn geven zeyer barimt, vayl di hale draytsn hot bagrobn tsener, tsener toyznte yidn.

00:25:13.424 --> 00:25:14.265
ikh hob gearbet,

00:25:14.265 --> 00:25:15.967
vos hot, vos hot men dortn getun?

00:25:16.310 --> 00:25:18.518
yeder tish fun fir mentshn iz geven a

00:25:18.518 --> 00:25:20.388
TEAM arbet, veyst vos heyst TEAM arbet.

00:25:21.423 --> 00:25:24.674
un an andere opteylung zenen gevezn froyen vos zey hobn gevoygn,

00:25:25.068 --> 00:25:26.770
BEDIYUK gevoygn azelkhene

00:25:26.770 --> 00:25:27.917
biselekh mel.

00:25:27.917 --> 00:25:30.288
se hot geheysn PIKRIN aza fa- aza min

00:25:30.288 --> 00:25:31.239
a grine,

00:25:32.510 --> 00:25:35.486
un zey hobn, in yede pres, yede

00:25:35.497 --> 00:25:37.550
fir mentshn hot gehat ire ⟨vegerin⟩.

00:25:38.197 --> 00:25:39.797
un zey hobn undz tsugegebn

00:25:39.797 --> 00:25:45.329
di yedn por minut aza min dos, mit ikh veys nisht vifl se iz gevezn, a tsen oder tsvontsik shiselekh,

00:25:46.314 --> 00:25:48.434
se iz geven aza forem fun shtol,

00:25:49.672 --> 00:25:51.235
di shtol iz geven azoy dik,

00:25:51.612 --> 00:25:53.896
der sh- hot zikh tseteylt in tsvey teyln.

00:25:53.907 --> 00:25:56.652
di ineveynik a firekekhdike lokh,

00:25:56.877 --> 00:26:01.034
un me hot tseteylt iz gevezn a halbn di un a halbn di. vos hot, vos hot men getun?

00:26:01.034 --> 00:26:05.093
me hot tsuzamengenumen dem di shti- dos, di tsvey oyf aza min,

00:26:05.129 --> 00:26:06.777
hintn iz geven a ⟨badn⟩

00:26:07.660 --> 00:26:09.582
un me hot arayngeshit dem puder,

00:26:09.582 --> 00:26:11.874
frier hot men arayngeshlept epes aza min tsinder,

00:26:11.964 --> 00:26:13.510
me hot arayngeshit dem puder,

00:26:13.651 --> 00:26:16.525
me hot arayngeshtelt a korek, oykhet aza shtikn,

00:26:16.525 --> 00:26:18.910
un aroyfgetun a ring, der ring iz gevezn oykhet,

00:26:18.984 --> 00:26:21.864
der der MACHSHIR aleyn hot gevoygn,

00:26:22.291 --> 00:26:24.378
me hot im nisht gekent oyfheybn, me hot geritsht,

00:26:24.620 --> 00:26:26.032
oyf oyf eyl.

00:26:26.088 --> 00:26:27.466
vayl er iz geven zeyer shver.

00:26:28.299 --> 00:26:32.337
iz eyner hot arayngeshit, er hot gegebn dem tsveytn, arayngezetst dem korek, er hot gegebn dem dritn,

00:26:32.337 --> 00:26:35.189
ikh, un eyn- eyner iz geven der preser. vos heyst a preser?

00:26:35.200 --> 00:26:37.139
ikh bin geven a preser, ikh bin geven a giber.

00:26:37.139 --> 00:26:37.856
a kleyner.

00:26:37.856 --> 00:26:39.447
ober ikh ho- ikh bin geven zeyer geshikt.

00:26:40.465 --> 00:26:43.143
me hot arayngerukt dem dem forem oyf aza min,

00:26:43.554 --> 00:26:45.719
hot zikh geglitsht oyf aza min shtol,

00:26:45.764 --> 00:26:48.509
arayngerukt in, in azoy vi in an oyvn arayn,

00:26:49.595 --> 00:26:52.188
me hot tsugemakht an ayzerne tir mit a hentl,

00:26:52.818 --> 00:26:55.566
un bay a, un a hidronishe pres, me hot bay a ruk,

00:26:55.566 --> 00:26:58.004
bay aza hentl, hot zikh aropgelozt a pres,

00:26:58.049 --> 00:27:00.372
un arayngerukt dem, er hot arayngerukt dem korek,

00:27:00.597 --> 00:27:05.100
un se iz aroysge- me hot, ikh hob im tsurik aroysgenumen hob ikh im untergegebn an andern, er hot aroysgehakt dem korek,

00:27:05.100 --> 00:27:06.593
un er hot aroysgenumen a shteyndl.

00:27:06.593 --> 00:27:07.614
a tsuzamen-geprest,

00:27:07.614 --> 00:27:08.793
dos iz geven a mine.

00:27:09.339 --> 00:27:12.927
fun di andere zayt iz gevezn fray. ofn.

00:27:13.169 --> 00:27:17.908
ober fun eyn pres tsum tsveytn iz gevezn mit a beton, zeyer a dike vant beton,

00:27:17.945 --> 00:27:20.094
un dortn iz gevezn a dike vant beton.

00:27:20.094 --> 00:27:20.979
far vos?

00:27:20.979 --> 00:27:23.525
vayl a sakh, se iz gevezn zeyer a sakh mol oyfraysn.

00:27:23.682 --> 00:27:25.131
far vos iz geven an oyfrays?

00:27:25.134 --> 00:27:28.081
az me hot nisht oysgereynikt gut dem dem

00:27:28.829 --> 00:27:30.877
dem dos di MACHSHIR,

00:27:30.147 --> 00:27:31.139
di formen

00:27:30.877 --> 00:27:31.653
di forem,

00:27:31.653 --> 00:27:36.468
un der korek hot zikh nisht arayngerukt azoy, hot er gegebn a krats a bisl, se hot zikh gemakht a funk,

00:27:36.609 --> 00:27:38.189
un se hot oys- an eksplozye.

00:27:38.465 --> 00:27:39.905
vos hot men getun demolt?

00:27:39.916 --> 00:27:43.707
me hot genumen di ale fir mentshn, me hot zey oysgeshtelt in droysn, me hot zey avekgeshosn.

00:27:44.590 --> 00:27:46.481
me hot arayngenumen andere mentshn.

00:27:46.869 --> 00:27:47.904
azoy iz gevezn

00:27:47.904 --> 00:27:52.044
vos ikh hob aykh gezogt di di tsvey maysters, eyner iz geven oyf bay tog, eyner bay nakht.

00:27:52.218 --> 00:27:54.237
se iz gevezn tsvey, tsvey shikhtn.

00:27:54.513 --> 00:27:57.511
tsvelef sho bay tog un tsvelef sho bay nakht un nokh epes getoysht,

00:27:57.635 --> 00:27:59.767
nakher zenen di geven bay nakht, zey zenen geven bay tog,

00:27:59.767 --> 00:28:00.442
azoy,

00:28:00.442 --> 00:28:02.053
undz ho'mir gemuzt makhn a norme.

00:28:02.053 --> 00:28:04.126
se iz gevezn dakht zikh mir fuftsn kestlekh,

00:28:04.216 --> 00:28:05.375
oyb ikh gedenk.

00:28:05.499 --> 00:28:07.180
ontsufiln fuftsn kestlekh.

00:28:08.620 --> 00:28:10.302
di hale hob, hot,

00:28:10.831 --> 00:28:13.239
ikh bin di eyntsike, se iz gevezn nokh a yid,

00:28:14.020 --> 00:28:17.964
ober er hot nisht in di hale, er iz gevezn fun transport, er hot gebrengt di kestlekh

00:28:18.020 --> 00:28:22.177
fun UNK er hot aropgelodevet fun di oytos di kestlekh di pikrin.

00:28:22.205 --> 00:28:24.629
dem KHOMER, tsu makhn dem,

00:28:24.804 --> 00:28:26.334
er iz do geshtorbn in Yisroel.

00:28:28.246 --> 00:28:30.184
di hale hobn,

00:28:30.184 --> 00:28:33.134
dortn hot men nisht gekent mer oyshaltn vi etlekhe

00:28:33.292 --> 00:28:34.282
etlekhe vokhn.

00:28:34.355 --> 00:28:36.307
ikh hob dortn gearbet kimat a tsvey yor.

00:28:36.768 --> 00:28:38.298
vi azoy, fregt mikh nisht.

00:28:39.097 --> 00:28:41.808
koydem kol hobn zey undz gegebn maskes ontsutun,

00:28:41.982 --> 00:28:44.103
vayl es iz, dos alts iz geven biter vi gal.

00:28:44.986 --> 00:28:48.164
ober mir hobn bald aropgevorfn di maskes vayl me hot nisht gekent otemen,

00:28:48.164 --> 00:28:50.122
un se hot zikh gemakht do ranes.

00:28:50.167 --> 00:28:53.671
koydem kol di hent zenen geven in gantsn tseshpoltn fun, biz tsu di beyner.

00:28:54.402 --> 00:28:55.915
mir zenen geven grin

00:28:57.237 --> 00:28:59.409
azoy vi ir zet, ot di kolir hobn undz gehat.

00:28:59.499 --> 00:29:00.792
ir zet di kolir?

00:29:01.929 --> 00:29:03.054
gel-grin.

00:29:02.722 --> 00:29:04.583
gel-grin, mamesh der gantse,

00:29:04.583 --> 00:29:06.749
afile di vayslekh fun di oygn zenen geven gel.

00:29:08.290 --> 00:29:10.158
dortn hob ikh gearbet tsvey yor,

00:29:10.299 --> 00:29:14.056
di ha- me hot arayngenumen, se iz gekumen a transport fun holendishe yidn.

00:29:15.226 --> 00:29:16.135
fun Holand.

00:29:16.171 --> 00:29:19.524
gezunte nokh, dos iz geven nayntsn dray un fertsik oyb ikh hob nisht keyn toes.

00:29:20.170 --> 00:29:25.914
me hot, me hot undz aroysgenumen in droysn, tsu tseklapn dortn di UNK vos zenen geven nisht gut, hot men tseklapt vider oyf un ⟨nakher nokh⟩,

00:29:25.942 --> 00:29:29.041
se iz nisht di laykht arbet in droysn, me hot zey avekgezetst.

00:29:29.722 --> 00:29:32.365
in meshekh fun etlekhe vokhn iz nisht geblibn keyn eyner fun zey.

00:29:33.502 --> 00:29:35.279
zey zenen, zey hobn nisht gekent mer oyshaltn.

00:29:35.290 --> 00:29:36.905
vayl alts iz gevezn biter vi,

00:29:36.961 --> 00:29:38.103
biter vi gal.

00:29:38.699 --> 00:29:40.578
dos gantse lebn iz gevezn biter.

00:29:40.578 --> 00:29:43.582
yede zakh vos me hot gegebn, di portsye broyt mit a bisl zup,

00:29:43.610 --> 00:29:45.174
vos me hot gegesn iz geven biter.

00:29:47.542 --> 00:29:50.743
bald veln mir oyfhern un aribergeyn tsu di nekste kasete.
